snippet.textDisplay: There was a thought I was working on/ thinking: It was about cells in general in the body. If one knows say certain aspect of a virus, such as how its eletron bonds are bound... Could one destroy the virus through disrupting its unique magnetic system. Most life is super resistent to being volitile from electro magnetic pulse or energy or similar type.. but that could be a good thing, since it would allow one to focus or attack isolated or grouped viruses that have certain field. this idea is more theory.. or sic fi and completely against destroying a virus by traditional means.. this is more like discombobulating the entire entity from existence. :D and the material can be absorbed into the body.
